AEditor version 1.x
===================

This application is a programmers editor. 

You may find screenshots here:
http://aeditor.rubyforge.org/wiki/wiki.pl?MainThemes


Features
========

  1. syntax coloring for:  ruby, c++. 

  2. multiple buffers.

  3. undo/redo and macros.

  4. easy to make color themes.

  5. ruby configuration file.

  6. written entirely in ruby.

  7. ruby license.

  8. crossplatform: unix, windows, mac.

  9. has 2 default keymaps: cua and simon.

 10. windowmode/fullscreen mode.

 11. unittested:  446 tests, 1532 assertions.


---------------
End of document
